{"id":19287,"date":"2014-06-07T18:55:18","date_gmt":"2014-06-07T14:55:18","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=19287"},"modified":"2019-05-27T12:22:38","modified_gmt":"2019-05-27T08:22:38","slug":"tasbih-istighfar-ten-times","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/06\/07\/tasbih-istighfar-ten-times\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Praise: Glorify Allah, seek forgiveness ten times"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Salma Umm Rafi\u2019 reported: She said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, teach me some words, but not too much for me.\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>Say Allah is the greatest ten times. Allah Almighty will say: This is for me. Say glory be to Allah ten times. Allah Almighty will say: This is for me. Say: O Allah forgive me. Allah will say: I have done so. If you say it ten times, Allah will say each time: I have done so.<\/strong>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r 20260<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Sahih<\/em><\/strong>\u00a0<em><strong>li ghayrihi<\/strong><\/em> (authentic due to external evidence) according to Al-Albani<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0649 \u0623\u064f\u0645\u0651\u0650 \u0628\u064e\u0646\u0650\u064a \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0631\u064e\u0627\u0641\u0650\u0639\u064d \u0645\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u064a\u064e\u0627 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u062e\u0652\u0628\u0650\u0631\u0652\u0646\u0